description:
Major mixed use redevelopment proposal comprising 332 apartments, office space, A1 to A3 uses and live/work units within four separate buildings above under croft parking. Including a 23 storey landmark tower fronting Ilford Hill and Chapel Road.  Landscaped amenity and car parking.
MAJOR APPLICATION
decision_conditions: Before the development hereby permitted commences, a plan which clearly designates the separate areas of 'residential' and 'work' areas of the live work units shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority.  The development shall be completed in accordance with these approved details.
